column59: confusion keeping track of how much to give to each person relative to what i gave someone else.  i think it would have been easier to give each person an equal amount.
Would have been nice to have a table so could have done comparison easier.
Difficult to make so many fine distinctions, but the survey got me thinking ... thanks!
1st question would not allow me to give over 100 dollars or 10 hours. If numbers were larger than that I could not advance to the next question.
No issues. I had to really think about the people I am close to, whether they are relatives or not.
